channel.title: Implementing and using 2.01
channel.description: I'd be interested to hear experiences from people who have either produced or are using 2.01 data. Maybe you're a data publisher who has adapted your systems to produce 2.01, so please tell us what you had to change. Or maybe you're a data consumer who has had to adapt your app to pull in 2.01 data, so how did you do that?
